snippet: Pro-Palestinian French youth defying a ban on a protest against Israel's Gaza offensive clashed with police Sunday, setting fire to cars, pillaging stores and attacking two synagogues in Paris suburbs....

headline.print_headline: French Youth, Police Clash at Anti-Israeli Protest
headline.main: French Youth, Police Clash at Anti-Israeli Protest

lead_paragraph: Pro-Palestinian French youth defying a ban on a protest against Israel's Gaza offensive clashed with police Sunday, setting fire to cars, pillaging stores and attacking two synagogues in Paris suburbs.
